h3. Bug

When creating an Issue Collector in JIRA and adding the "Components" field to it, the dropdown feature doesn't work in this field.

h3. Steps to reproduce

# Create an Issue Collector;
# Add the "Components" field to it;
# Add this Issue Collector as an Announcement Banner for testing;
# Open the Announcement Banner and click on the dropdown option in the "Components" field;

h3. Workaround

Change the render of the "Components" field from "Auto Complete Renderer" to "Select List Renderer". This will get this problem to work with a select list instead of the dropdown.

(i) This also occurs with the "Priority" field, but this is already reported in [JRA-30051|https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRA-30051].
(i) This also affect the *Affect Version/s* field.

